"""
CFBD Auto-Fetcher
=================
Pulls college stats and draft data from the College Football Data API
and feeds them directly into the dynasty model.

Usage:
    python cfbd_fetcher.py --players "Malik Nabers,Rome Odunze,Brock Bowers" --year 2024
    python cfbd_fetcher.py --file my_players.txt --year 2025
    python cfbd_fetcher.py --draft-class 2024        # pull entire post-draft class
    python cfbd_fetcher.py --prospects --year 2026   # pre-draft: college stats only
    python cfbd_fetcher.py --prospects --file prospects.txt --year 2026

API key loaded from .env file (CFBD_API_KEY) or environment variable.
"""

